title: Mushroom monster girl
description: Monster mushroom girl character variant for the game
longDescription:
The model is made according to the identical dimensions of the mannequin (all joints of the shoulder of the finger and the rest are the same size as the mannequin), which makes it possible to use all standard animations without any distortion. The model is also modular, has 6 sets of unique textures

animation;

3x pose

8x walking

3x attack

1x Dying

1x fear

1x hit

3x idle

1x rage

3x run

1x talk

1x Transition
